(;SZ[19]AW[pb][pc][pd][qe][re][qg][rg]AB[qb][qc][qd][rd][pe][pf]LB[jj:?]C[If White moves first, how many liberties does the Black corner group have?]PL[W];W[jj];AE[jj]LB[ra:A]C[RIGHT
Five.  It will take White five moves to remove the Black stones.  First White plays at A and then Black has a maximum of 4 liberties remaining.])